item.title: OWN - Oprah's Compelling Commencement Speech To TSU Class of 2023
item.description: Video Transcript Friends, faculty, family, and the Tennessee State University class of 2023. [CHEERING] Who says you can’t go home again? Because I’m back. Dr. Glenda Glover is the reason why I’m here, because she is relentless. You actually– you don’t know the meaning of no. And she’s been here a decade and has been asking me for a decade. I’ve been to so many graduations since I have 20 daughters
